<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=8994&amp;p=95277#p95277"><![CDATA[
SNES does not have any special specs for maps, it is purely software thing - i.e. SNES does not handle large level maps automatically. So a plugin would be needed, to export the data into format of your map engine.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4205">Shiru</a> — Sun Jun 10, 2012 1:28 pm</p><hr />
